{
  "stem": "7273.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to organized a wire cutter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Little wire cutter, what we needed for the machines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just grabbed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And with this wire cutter, I cut a hole in the fence, behind-- actually, behind the [INAUDIBLE] station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with her, we had practically nothing with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A little bag.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "With her, at night time, we slipped through this hole.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She's panicked a bit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I go back, tell her, all right, I'll go forward.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- we went then through a journey where German gardens.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We jumped the fence and banked through the garden into the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my first-- our first way was to the station, away from where the [INAUDIBLE] was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had good luck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had good luck in that at the same night, when we went to the station and boarded the train, this train came from a ways, with refugees from Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hamburg was completely bombarded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was, for us, good luck, that nobody checked for papers, for it mostly would have been done.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I listened to the conversations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So straightforward, I said, I'm from Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you had a ready-made situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, for me, actually, it happened to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Therefore I say I was meant to live.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because otherwise, it would have been so much harder.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, when I-- before I went away, or ran away from the camp, I said, honey, I can buy some bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could you give me my money?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she gave it to the last cent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No question asked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had some money for tickets and eventually to buy something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
